<div class="mw-heading mw-heading3"><h3 id="Diagonals_and_bimedians">Diagonals and bimedians</h3><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Quadrilateral&amp;action=edit&amp;section=20" title="Edit section: Diagonals and bimedians"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
